text: Eye liner is a cosmetic used to define the eyes. Eyeliner may also refer to: * Eyeliner (band), an Indonesian rock band (1998-now) * Eyeliner (UK band), a British rock band (2008-now) * The Eyeliners, a punk rock band from Albuquerque, New Mexico, US * Musion Eyeliner, a high-definition video projection system for stage productions
title: Eyeliner (disambiguation)
